OL,3,CTreasures found buried with 'Iron Age
OL,4,Cwarrior' to go on show for first time
OL,6,FRare treasures found with a young Iron
OL,7,FAge man buried around 2,000 years ago
OL,8,Fare to go on show for the first time
OL,9,Fin a new exhibition.
OL,11,FThe remains of the man, who was aged
OL,12,Fbetween 17 and 25, were discovered in
OL,13,Fa stone-lined cist at Marshill in
OL,14,FAlloa.
OL,16,FHe was buried with an iron sword in a
OL,17,Fleather scabbard placed carefully
OL,18,Facross his chest, and a spear laid
OL,19,Falongside him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
