PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782413298
OL,3,CTreasures found buried with 'Iron Age
OL,4,Cwarrior' to go on show for first time
OL,6,FThe young man, who was buried around
OL,7,F10-70AD, was richly adorned with
OL,8,Fornaments including a bronze cloak
OL,9,Fpin, a glass bead pendant and bronze
OL,10,Fand iron rings from a belt around his
OL,11,Fwaist.
OL,13,FTwo bronze toe rings suggest he wore
OL,14,Fsandals, which was a sign of high
OL,15,Fstatus.
OL,17,FExperts say burying someone with
OL,18,Fweapons may have reflected their role
OL,19,Fin life as a warrior, or how their
OL,20,Fcommunity wanted them to be seen in
OL,21,Fthe afterlife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
