PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782413298
OL,3,CTreasures found buried with 'Iron Age
OL,4,Cwarrior' to go on show for first time
OL,6,FThe objects will go on show in the
OL,7,Fexhibition Scotland's First Warriors,
OL,8,Fwhich opens on Saturday at the
OL,9,FNational Museum of Scotland in
OL,10,FEdinburgh.
OL,12,FVery few Iron Age burials have been
OL,13,Fdiscovered in Scotland and those
OL,14,Fincluding weapons are said to be
OL,15,Fexceptionally rare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782413298
OL,3,CTreasures found buried with 'Iron Age
OL,4,Cwarrior' to go on show for first time
OL,6,FMatthew Knight, senior curator of
OL,7,Fprehistory at National Museums
OL,8,FScotland, said: "The remarkable
OL,9,Fobjects from the Marshill burial give
OL,10,Fus a vivid insight into the mindset of
OL,11,Fprehistoric communities living in
OL,12,FScotland almost 2,000 years ago.
OL,14,F"Burying people with weapons may
OL,15,Freflect the person's role in life as a
OL,16,Fwarrior, or how their community wanted
OL,17,Fthem to be seen in the afterlife.
OL,19,F"These treasured objects tell us this
OL,20,Fyoung man was a powerful member of his
OL,21,Fcommunity.
OL,26,@pD@QOUvD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
