OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782413298
OL,3,CTreasures found buried with 'Iron Age
OL,4,Cwarrior' to go on show for first time
OL,6,FThey have undergone significant
OL,7,Fresearch and conservation by experts
OL,8,Fat the National Museums Collection
OL,9,FCentre in Edinburgh and are on loan to
OL,10,Fthe exhibition from the Treasure Trove
OL,11,FUnit.
OL,13,FReplicas of the spearhead and sword
OL,14,Fhave been created for the exhibition
OL,15,Fby Ratho Byres Forge and Alan Braby.
OL,17,FThey will be displayed alongside the
OL,18,Foriginals to illustrate how they would
OL,19,Fonce have gleamed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
