FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1782413298
OL,3,CTreasures found buried with 'Iron Age
OL,4,Cwarrior' to go on show for first time
OL,6,FThe free exhibition, which runs until
OL,7,FMay 16 next year, will look at the
OL,8,Forigins of organised conflict.
OL,10,FIt will explore how people fought,
OL,11,Ftheir motivations, the impact of war
OL,12,Fon people's lives, and the long-
OL,13,Flasting legacy of prehistoric conflict.
OL,15,FItems which have never been seen
OL,16,Fbefore including internationally
OL,17,Fsignificant archaeological discoveries
OL,18,Ffrom across Scotland, such as the
OL,19,FCarnoustie Hoard, will also be on show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
